<inglise> (a) a report on the implementation of this Regulation, its contribution to the development of Community environmental policy, and the use made of the appropriations as well as, where appropriate, proposals for any adjustments to be made with a view to continuing the action beyond the third phase; </inglise>
<eesti> a) aruande k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse rakendamise kohta, selle m&otilde;just &uuml;henduse keskkonnapoliitikale ja assigneeringute kasutamisest ning vajaduse korral ettepanekute kohta v&otilde;imalikest muudatustest tegevuse j&auml;tkamiseks kolmanda etapi l&otilde;ppemise j&auml;rel; </eesti>
<inglise> (b) if appropriate, a proposal concerning a fourth phase of LIFE. </inglise>
