<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The European Parliament and the Council, acting in accordance with the Treaty, shall decide no later than 1 July 2004 on the implementation of the fourth phase as from 1 January 2005. </inglise>
